---
const {pageTitle, articleTitle, articleP, articleImg, background} = Astro.props;
---

<section class="hero-container">
  <section class="hero-content">
    <article>
      <h2>GUIDE TIL BÆREDYGTIGT FORBRUG: forstå produkt&shymærkningerne</h2>
      <p>
        Dankort giver dig med Forbrugs&shytjekket mulighed for at få et overblik over lorem ipsum
        dolor sit amet. Ut voluptatibus dolorem sit quia maxime eos voluptatem accusantium qui quod
        necessitatibus sit earum maiores ut amet consequuntur aut quod aspernatur.
      </p>
      <a class="cta-grey" href="/">Læs artikel</a>
    </article>
    <img src="/oekotex.png" alt="OEKO-TEX-mærkat" />
  </section>
</section>

<style>
  h1 {
    text-align: center;
    background-color: var(--primary-color);
    padding-top: var(--top-padding);
    color: var(--black-color);
  }

  h2,
  p {
    color: var(--white-color);
  }

  h2 {
    padding-bottom: calc(var(--top-padding) * 2);
  }

  .hero-container {
    background-color: var(--primary-color);
    background-image: url(/dandelions.png);
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    padding: var(--main-padding) var(--main-padding);
  }

  .hero-content {
    background-color: var(--secondary-color);
    border-radius: 10px;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    padding: var(--main-padding);
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  article {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    max-width: 480px;
  }

  img {
    max-width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    margin-left: var(--main-padding);
  }

  a {
    align-self: flex-start;
    display: inline-block;
    width: auto;
  }

  p {
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--top-padding) * 2);
  }

  @media (max-width: 1330px) {
    .hero-container {
      padding: var(--main-padding) 0;
    }

    .hero-content {
      border-radius: 0;
      gap: calc(var(--article-gap) / 2);
      padding: var(--main-padding) calc(var(--main-padding) / 2);
    }

    img {
      margin-left: 0;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 450px) {
    .article {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    a {
      align-self: center;
    }
  }
</style>
